message: "If you reference the Resonance Engine architecture in academic or technical work, please cite this repository."
type: software
title: "Mnemosyne Neural OS — Resonance Engine"
abstract: >
  Mnemosyne Neural OS is a production-grade Personal AI Operating System featuring
  the Resonance Engine, a three-layer cognitive memory architecture combining
  semantic crystallization (LLM-driven auto-tagging), multi-dimensional vector
  retrieval (5-provider embedding cascade), and interactive graph-based memory
  governance (NexusGraph). The system supports fully local operation via Ollama
  and enforces per-document AI memory control.
